segment.source: You can use the procedures in this section to configure and manage the Microsoft Application Virtualization (App-V) Client.
segment.target: You can use the procedures in this section to configure and manage the Microsoft Application Virtualization (App-V) Client.

segment.source: Procedures are provided for manual interaction with the App-V Client by using the App-V Client Management Console and also by using the command line.
segment.target: Procedures are provided for manual interaction with the App-V Client by using the App-V Client Management Console and also by using the command line.
